title: 2nd Senior level UK vaccine program whistleblower speaks out - Brand New Tube
cleaned_text:
⁣A 2nd senior level insider from the UK NHS Vaccine programme rollout has now come forward to speak out about what is really going on behind the scenes of the vaccine rollout. Severe adverse events are not only very common, they are going unreported due to either willful negligence or just because Doctors and Nurses are unaware of either the symptoms to look out for or even more alarmingly, they have no idea what the UK gov adverse event reporting system is ie: The Yellow Card Scheme. 

This is now the 2nd senior leve NHS insider to say that what is happening is nothing short of GENOCIDE! 

Please do share to any and all platforms 

Source: ukcolumn.org
